msgid "Arturia KeyLab 88"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/arturia_keylab_mk1.md:19
msgid ""
"The Arturia KeyLab 88 (retroactively called the \"Mark 1\") is a full size "
"piano keyboard that includes various encoders, faders, buttons, and velocity"
" sensitive touch pads. It also includes a two-line dot-matrix display."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/arturia_keylab_mk1.md:25
msgid ""
"Arturia also made 61 and 25 key versions of this keyboard. This mapping has "
"only been tested with the full size version and it is unknown whether it "
"works for the smaller versions."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/arturia_keylab_mk1.md:29
msgid "Menu Controls"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/arturia_keylab_mk1.md:32
msgid ""
"On the left side of the controller is an unlabeled section of controls "
"surrounding the screen and the KeyLab logo. These global controls are used "
"to select the deck, and to perform various tasks using the built-in menu "
"which will be displayed on the screen."
