#: ../../hardware/controllers/arturia_keylab_mk1.md:192
msgid "Drum Pads"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/arturia_keylab_mk1.md:195
msgid ""
"To the right of the main controls are a collection of 16 drum pads that are "
"individually labeled Pad 16 (top right) through Pad 1 (bottom left). In "
"Mixxx we invert the numbers so that eg. Pad 13 in the top left maps to "
"Sampler 1. If the pad is not illuminated, pressing it will load the "
"currently selected track into the given sampler. If it is illuminated, "
"pressing it will cause the sampler to play and the pad to blink for the "
"duration of the playback. The pads are velocity sensitive and the harder "
"they are hit the louder the volume of the sampler."
msgstr ""

